{"tid":1016788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州運動員宣誓 遭批評普通話不標準 付海峰：你來廣州就要感受廣州文化","createTime":"2019-02-11T03:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T12:01:59.000Z","uid":144372,"like":246,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"404bf0b79137a7fb7cf33cff4f69e706d74f497e","tid":1016788,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.badmintoncn.com/newsm-view-12047-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.badmintoncn.com%2Fnewsm-view-12047-1.html&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5yJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=d3e6d5e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.badmintoncn.com/newsm-view-12047-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n開幕式今晚進行，羽毛球名將傅海峰代表運動員宣誓。當觀眾們為傅海峰的普通話發音&ldquo;擔憂&rdquo;時，他笑著表示：&ldquo;來廣州，就應該讓大家感受一下粵系普通話。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n出色的成績，俊朗的外型，又是土生土長的廣東人，註定傅海峰會成為開幕式現場的重要角色。&ldquo;大概在兩個月之前吧，就有通知我，讓我做好準備當運動員代表。&rdquo;傅海峰說，&ldquo;不過，也沒有完全確定，直到來廣州之後才確定。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n當被問起有沒有為了宣誓而練練普通話時，傅海峰笑著回答：&ldquo;大家來到廣州，就要感受一下粵系普通話嘛。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"c0637b0ab2d3366e79ee963d8cbb5895bcbe9662","tid":1016788,"uid":144372,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"運動員打波唔知關普通話咩事<br />\n外國大把運動員口齒不清<br />\n打到波咪得"},{"pid":"c7af33475bd3efe1d89e27ff7e69f87a07b8b6ce","tid":1016788,"uid":7355,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"好難服侍 講廣東話又屌 講蝗語唔正又屌"},{"pid":"a47cd8b491dd836ce15efbd6974f07cc7705223e","tid":1016788,"uid":143499,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"開幕式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本人??"},{"pid":"69b664f5ba2c75f014eef7203c2b31a23a11f109","tid":1016788,"uid":144372,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"c7af33475bd3efe1d89e27ff7e69f87a07b8b6ce","tid":1016788,"uid":7355,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"好難服侍 講廣東話又屌